videos.description: Back-to-back steals lead to Kyle Guy landing a 3 point jumper for Virginia.
videos.headline: Back-to-back steals lead to 3 for UVA

videos.description: London Perrantes takes a shot from deep and earns 3 for Virginia.

videos.headline: Perrantes lands 3 pointer off pass from Jerome
